  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicNavigator
    superclass for navigatior.
    Claw
    the claw class only serves 2 purposes: controlling the claw and the lift
    ColorPoller
    class used for fetching data from the light sensors
    Constants
    class containing all constant values
    Filters
    all data filters for data from the us sensors and wifi
    LeftColorController
    This class is used to process color data of both side light sensors for odometry correction
    Main
    Team 13's final DPM project.
    Navigation
    the navigation class is used to move the robot during localization
    Navigator
    The Navigator class extends the functionality of the Navigation class.
    ObstacleAvoidance
    Class that allows the robot to do obstacle avoidance and pick up blocks
    Odometer
    The odometer is used to keep track of the robot's positino on the field
    OdometryCorrection
    Odometry correction to corect the robot's heading by detecting black lines using the light sensor on the field.
    SideColorController
    the side color controllers are used to process data from the 2 side light sensors
    SideUSController
    The side ultrasonic controllers are used to get data from all three ultrasonic sensors using a median filter
    UltrasonicPoller
    used for fetching samples directly from the ultrasonic sensors without applying any filter other than letting the max distance being 255
    USLocalizer
    class used to localize the robot from a corner on the field and move it to 0,0 using falling edge (rising edge isn't actually implemented)
    WifiTest2
    class used for connecting the robot to the DPM wifi server
